c3ddd4cd154d779730b86","tid":203554,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"加奶落蛋液<br />\n油落鍋<br />\n大火熱左個底<br />\n蛋落鍋<br />\n轉細火<br />\n翻兩翻<br />\n完成"},{"pid":"94fb9e56f0d2e6e35e85d43345100eb0f533e890","tid":203554,"uid":55419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔落雨炒就點都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落雨千其唔好炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好大鑊"},{"pid":"b53b581ef3ae0aab043e44ccbe4399a2dcd56fd6","tid":203554,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔落雨炒就點都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落雨千其唔好炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好大鑊</blockquote><br />\n屌 死撚開啦屌你老母<br />\n係咪好撚好笑呀 仆街"},{"pid":"8fe65a58c571e4bec118aab9a2c58315fe00300e","tid":203554,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔落雨炒就點都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落雨千其唔好炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好大鑊</blockquote><br />\n你呢啲人其實幾撚多歲？<br />\n好笑咩？"},{"pid":"33ce380d357d77bfe20fb58642cc61b813eff25a","tid":203554,"uid":33258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落雨嗰時 蒐集啲雨水 落鍋</blockquote><br />\n咁既說話都講得出 小心被人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d205375120c029dc291767726ba2d8f47412c78","tid":203554,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔落雨炒就點都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落雨千其唔好炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好大鑊</blockquote><br />\n屌 死撚開啦屌你老母<br />\n係咪好撚好笑呀 仆街</blockquote><br />\n討論質素每況愈下咪多得你班撚樣囉<br />\n正正經經討論點炒蛋 你就係懶幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da188b1a759cc55dd55785a219a6988a8e9b193","tid":203554,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>落雨嗰時 蒐集啲雨水 落鍋</blockquote><br />\n咁既說話都講得出 小心被人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b500979df6850aac38245ff14c7188aca9d02ae","tid":203554,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加奶落蛋液<br />\n油落鍋<br />\n大火熱左個底<br />\n蛋落鍋<br />\n轉細火<br />\n翻兩翻<br />\n完成</blockquote><br />\n打蛋要打幾耐 我想整到大快活果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dfea75b8da8dc7fae46d5b6da87cd943bd845a","tid":203554,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"I加牛奶"},{"pid":"e2398d67ad3be7c8bfc59e19f20805331554ef34","tid":203554,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>落雨嗰時 蒐集啲雨水 落鍋</blockquote><br />\n咁既說話都講得出 小心被人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收撚皮啦你屌你老母"},{"pid":"bca48378a02f47ce28151f84c1053d3b2954abcf","tid":203554,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"<b